<div class="blog-post-home">
    <a href="/dashboard/blog/{{userPostData.id}}">
        <h3>{{userPostData.title}}</h3>
    </a>
    <p>{{userPostData.description}}</p>
</div>

<form class="update-blog-post">
    <p>Need to edit? We've included the title and content of your blog post in the fields below so you can easily fix
        those pesky typos, or start over again completely. Just click in the input fields and edit away!</p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="twelve columns">
            <label for="blog-title">Your Previous Title</label>
            <input class="u-full-width" placeholder="A title goes here" id="blog-title-input"
                value="{{userPostData.title}}">
        </div>
        <div class="twelve columns">
            <label for="blog-content">Your Previous Blog Post Content</label>
            <textarea class="u-full-width" placeholder="This is the start of something amazing â€¦"
                id="blog-content-input">{{userPostData.description}}</textarea>
        </div>
        <input class="button-primary" type="submit" value="Update">
    </div>
</form>
<div class="delete-blog">
    <p>Need to delete your post completely? Just one click and then poff! It'll be gone. Forever.</p>
    <button id="delete-button">Delete</button>
</div>

<script src="../../js/updateblog.js"></script>